{"tid":1086172,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"學車問題","createTime":"2019-03-31T16:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T01:13:37.000Z","uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2a9314ab7ddd4d3da60dbfa1223ea28168815f3a","tid":1086172,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"學緊棍波<br />\n成撚日畀師傅屌我停得太急太大力<br />\n臨停之前我本身已經篤咗少少極力子同腳制，之後師傅由篤落d，搞到我真係要停嗰陣變到好chok，都唔知點樣滿足佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋你地停低係用空波定hold住用極力子加腳制?  <br />\n<br />\n一般行駕中減速係咪直接篤少少腳制黎減? 定會加埋極力子?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e73a5cc353dd418da5fbbf9b4347b3b0ceb940","tid":1086172,"uid":1837,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"盡早少少腳制 慢慢印慢架車 速度慢晒落黎再極力子"},{"pid":"8461a5eae77af7557e04f72be43faaee21861b76","tid":1086172,"uid":182178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:31:25.000Z","msg":"學車你就算見到綠燈都可以鬆定油門 實冇死"},{"pid":"70a9b11eb1ba69e0b11361f0ab6b715e570503fb","tid":1086172,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0e73a5cc353dd418da5fbbf9b4347b3b0ceb940","tid":1086172,"uid":1837,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"盡早少少腳制 慢慢印慢架車 速度慢晒落黎再極力子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:34:09.000Z","msg":"收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d461fbb127f7d31477a534b4b7949bd15379e3a4","tid":1086172,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8461a5eae77af7557e04f72be43faaee21861b76","tid":1086172,"uid":182178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:31:25.000Z","msg":"學車你就算見到綠燈都可以鬆定油門 實冇死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddb7c698e3da2f786401b7cc07aa5eb5d9f67bd","tid":1086172,"uid":208241,"like":5,"dis